    <JadeMethod name="delete" id="8c8e20c8-c37d-439f-8516-4f46e15ebf69">
        <updating/>
        <executionLocation>client</executionLocation>
        <source>delete() updating, clientExecution;
/*

Purpose:			

Parameters:			

Return Value:		

Date		Who		Reason
22 April 2013	cnwer1	Initial creation CCMS DPH 2280

